{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_04_01_short",
  "title": "神崎莉央 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "すずが歌った麻奈のカバー曲、評判がいいみたいね",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うまく歌えなくて悩んでいたすずの背中を\n莉央さんが押してくれたおかげです",
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "私は軽くアドバイスしただけよ。それに\nどちらかというと、もう一方の話題の方が面白かったし",
      "startTime": 13.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "すずがあんなことを考えていたなんて……\n凄く微笑ましかったわ",
      "startTime": 21.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "微笑ましいって、一体なんの話ですか？",
      "startTime": 23.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\n貴方には教えられないわね",
      "startTime": 29.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、ポテンシャルはあると思ってたけど\nちょっと助言しただけであそこまで歌えるなんて……",
      "startTime": 35.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "私達も負けていられないわね",
      "startTime": 39.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "同じ事務所の仲間とも張り合うなんて\n相変わらず負けず嫌いですね",
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、私達は負けない。星見プロは居心地がいいけど\nだからといって仲良しこよしをするつもりはないわ",
      "startTime": 52.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}